; href=&#34;#certified-kubernetes-administrator-cka---2025&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;It validates hands-on expertise in deploying, managing, and troubleshooting Kubernetes clusters in production environments.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
